Description: Target velocity for searching the switch.The adjustable value is internally limited to theparameter setting in RAMP_v_max.Modified settings become active the next time themotor moves.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 6099:1hModbus 10248Profibus 10248CIP 140.1.4ModbusTCP 10248EtherCAT 6099:1hPROFINET 10248

Description: Target velocity for moving away from switch.The adjustable value is internally limited to theparameter setting in RAMP_v_max.Modified settings become active the next time themotor moves.
Parameter address via fieldbus: CANopen 6099:2hModbus 10250Profibus 10250CIP 140.1.5ModbusTCP 10250EtherCAT 6099:2hPROFINET 10250
